{
  "title": "在Mac下用Sublime Text3 架设C开发环境",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">在Sublime Text中, 点击 Tools -&gt; Build System -&gt; New Build System... 会弹出一个配置文件的模版将模版中的内容替换成结果:</p><div class=\"toolbar\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\">for Mac:</div><div class=\"toolbar\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><br></div><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><br></div><div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><br></div><div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><br></div><div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><br></div><div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><br></div><div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><br></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><br></div></td><td class=\"code\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"line number1 index0 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">{</code></div><div class=\"line number2 index1 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"cmd\"</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"cpp plain\">:&nbsp;[</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"gcc\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">,&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"-o\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">,&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"$file_base_name\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">,&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"$file_name\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">],</code></div><div class=\"line number3 index2 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"cmd\"</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"cpp plain\">:&nbsp;[</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"./$file_base_name\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">],</code></div><div class=\"line number4 index3 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"selector\"</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"cpp plain\">:&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"source.c\"</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">,</code></div><div class=\"line number5 index4 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"shell\"</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"cpp plain\">:&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp keyword bold\">false</code><code class=\"cpp plain\">,</code></div><div class=\"line number6 index5 alt1\"><code class=\"cpp spaces\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"working_dir\"</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"cpp plain\">:&nbsp;</code><code class=\"cpp string\">\"$file_path\"</code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">}</code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\"><br></code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\"><br></code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\"><br></code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\">for windows:</code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\"><br></code></div><div class=\"line number7 index6 alt2\"><code class=\"cpp plain\"><pre class=\"lang-js prettyprint prettyprinted\"><code><span class=\"pun\">{</span><span class=\"pln\">\n    </span><span class=\"str\">\"cmd\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"str\">\"gcc\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"$file_name\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"-o\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"${file_base_name}.exe\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"&amp;&amp;\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"${file_base_name}.exe\"</span><span class=\"pun\">],</span><span class=\"pln\">\n    </span><span class=\"str\">\"selector\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"source.c\"</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">\n    </span><span class=\"str\">\"shell\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\">true</span><span class=\"pun\">,</span><span class=\"pln\">\n    </span><span class=\"str\">\"working_dir\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"pun\">:</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"str\">\"$file_path\"</span><span class=\"pln\">\n</span><span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></pre></code></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
    }
  ]
}